org.fhaes.model

Class FHFile

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.io.File
      • org.fhaes.model.FHFile
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<java.io.File>

    public class FHFile
extends java.io.File
    FHFile Class. Simple extension of java.io.File which includes functions for checking whether this is a valid FHX format file, and if not, to access the error reporting features of the DendroFileIO library.
